    <body>
      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Hold me in your arms</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>We've been trying for a long time</l>
          <l>To say what we want to say</l>
          <l>But feeling don't come easy</l>
          <l>To express in a simple way</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>But we all have feelings</l>
          <l>We all need loving</l>
          <l>And who would be the fool to say, that if you…</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>I won't feel better</l>
          <l>If you hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>We can brave this storm together.</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="4" type="stanza">
          <l>We both know there's a problem</l>
          <l>A problem that we've got to face</l>
          <l>So put your trust in me lover</l>
          <l>No-one's ever gonna take your place…</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="5" type="stanza">
          <l>'cos we all have a problem we all have fears</l>
          <l>But there's always got to be a way…</l>
          <l>Yes we all have feelings</l>
          <l>We all need loving</l>
          <l>And you would be a fool to say, that if you…</l>
        </lg>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="6" type="stanza">
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>I won't feel better</l>
          <l>If you hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>We can brave this storm together. </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="7" type="stanza">
          <l>You only have to hold me,</l>
          <l>Touch me, to make me feel so good,</l>
          <l>You only have to hold me,</l>
          <l>Feel me,</l>
          <l>To make me feel the way you know I shoul'd!!</l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="8" type="stanza">
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>When you gonna hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in youe arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms</l>
          <l>Hold me in your arms…………</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
